                    "text": "cracked windshield",
                    "colorize": true
                },
                {
                    "text": " that spread across half the glass within a week"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Dangerous because cracks impair visibility and weaken structural integrity. Often repairable if caught early; large cracks require full replacement."
        },
        {
