                {
                    "text": " on the highway and had to wait an hour for roadside assistance"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Caused by nails, glass, or worn rubber. Always carry a spare tire and know how to change it. 'Flat' here is adjective (not noun)."
        },
        {
