            "example": [
                {
                    "text": "Red wine left a stubborn "
                },
                {
                    "text": "stain",
                    "colorize": true
                },
                {
                    "text": " on the white tablecloth that wouldn't come out even after washing"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Act quickly on stains—blot (don't rub!) with cold water. Different stains need different treatments (grease vs. ink vs. wine)."
        },
        {
            "word": "loose",
            "wordType": "adjective",
            "definition": [
                {
                    "text": "Not firmly fixed in place; able to "
                },
                {
                    "text": "move or wobble",
