                },
                {
                    "text": " in the driver's side door"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Common on cars, refrigerators, and metal furniture. Small dents can sometimes be popped out with suction tools; larger ones need bodywork."
        },
        {
            "word": "filthy",
            "wordType": "adjective",
            "definition": [
                {
                    "text": "Extremely "
                },
                {
                    "text": "dirty or unclean",
                    "highlight": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "; covered in "
                },
                {
                    "text": "grime, dust, or stains",
